Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:07.11,Date - Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\blur8.351}Anno Domini 1985,\h Izumo\h
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že poslednou možnsťou je ho zabiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Avšak, čo ak to budú dvojčatá...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Čože, čo to vravíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Identické dvojčatá...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nebudeme vedieť, ktorý je ktorý.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Je mi to jedno!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Keď budem musieť, zabijem oboch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeho ambície v tomto svete budú márene\N tak dlho, ako bude existovať rod Asakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zober život toho novorodenca!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Odpusť mi, vnúčik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tak malý.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To teda —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On sa reinkarnoval spolu so strážcom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Niet pochýb...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To dieťa je —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otec, pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.77,magic,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Karalin-chou Karalin-sowaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.21,magic,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Horský bohovia Gohou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sú preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha... S niečím takým ma nikdy nechytíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kedy si...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Toto je... pred tisíckami rokov...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...veľký Onmyouji znenazdajky zmizol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Asakura Hao!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Som vďačný za tvoju ťažkú prácu pri mojom zrodení, Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo to hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zostaň pokojná!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stále máš jedno dieťa v sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Som si celkom istý, že moja druhá polovička si raz vyberie cestu, ktorá ju privedie ku kráľovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No a keď sa to stane,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sa ho zmocním
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a budem ešte silnejší!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Žiadny človek neujde svojmu osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bude to ťažké bremeno, ktoré bude musieť niesť, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Áno, žaidna iná voľba ako čeliť realite nezostáva.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toto{\i0} dieťa je naša jediná nádej!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.62,Narration,,0,0,0,,Potulné duše mŕtvych...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.96,Narration,,0,0,0,,Duchovia, ktorí dýchajú skrz stromy Zeme... bôžikovia a Budha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.59,Narration,,0,0,0,,Tí, ktorí s nimi dokážu voľne komunikovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:35.76,Narration,,0,0,0,,Trénovaním sily, ktorá v normálnych ľuďoch nedriema
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.18,Narration,,0,0,0,,...sa volajú šamani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:48.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Koeteyukou, kimi to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Kibou ni afureta mirai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.65,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Oshitsukerareteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.97,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Youi sareta yumetachi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Kokoro ga ugokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Soredemo mae e susume to iu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.68,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Omoi ni michibikarete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.96,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Fumidashita sono saki sekai ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.27,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:22.65,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Itetsuku koori wo tokaseru mono wa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:26.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Atsuku moesakaru tamashii
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Nemuraseteita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.63,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Mada minu chikara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.85,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Yobiokose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:36.05,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Daijoubu sa kurikaeshi tsubuyaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:39.56,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Kotoba wa chikara wo umidasu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Sokojikara ni wa, mada saki ga aru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.80,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Tsukinukero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:51.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Kokoro no zenryoku wa egao no tame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.04,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Namida no mukougawa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:04:02.80,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Koeteyukeru, kimi to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:48.51,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Prekročiť, s tebou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.15,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Budúcnosť plná nádeje
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.65,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Sa na mňa valí
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.97,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}S dlho pripravovanímy snami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.45,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}S bojujúcim srdcom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.21,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Ale pokračujem dopredu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.68,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Strážený mojimi túžbami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.96,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Ten moment keď vystúpime zo sveta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.27,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Zmena príde
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:22.65,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Budeme topiť mraziaci ľad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:26.15,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Srdce plniace sa vášňou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.35,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Vo mne prespáva
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.63,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Ešte nevídaná sila
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.85,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Prebuď ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:36.05,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Opakujúc šepot, v poriadku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:39.56,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Slovami prebúdzajúc takú silu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.87,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Odteraz, očakávaj viac!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.80,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Prelom to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:51.61,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}So všetkou silou v srdci priniesť úsmev
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.04,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Na druhom brehu sĺz
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:04:02.80,OP Translated,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.569}Môžem ísť ďalej, s tebou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.98,Date - Place,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)\blur8.351}O 13 rokov neskôr
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ach, to doučovanie sa pretiahlo. Prídem neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.70,sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.60\move(541,564.99,533,619.66,)\t(\fs40)}Zákaz\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hIba pre autorizovaný personál
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.70,sign,,0,0,0,,{\\frz21.60\t(\fs40)\move(905.01,778.32,829.81,783.12)}Hyakugan Cintorín
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,50,,{\pos(960,1070)}Ak mi ešte pamäť dobre slúži,\N tadiaľto vedie skratka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:22.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnAdobe Gothic Std B\shad4\c&H1E9BFF&\4c&H06040B&\pos(1394,933)\fad(900,900)}Episode 01\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\NChlapec, čo tancuje s duchmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mám zvláštny pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo sa tak ponáhľaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo ten týpek chce?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A čo tu robí tak neskoro celkom sám?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,M-mohol by to byť duch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Počkať...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dnešnú noc tu máme pekný výhľad na hviezdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bola by škoda neprísť a nepokochať sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme ich sledovať všetci spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hviezdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo by som sa mal na ne dívať?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Navyše, čo si myslel tým {\i1}všetci{\i0}? \NSme tu dvaja...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, je tu každý...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,z tohto pohrebiska!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, neboj sa, všetci sú moji kamoši!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aj keď to možno je banda idiotov,\N čo sa tu naveky zasekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz354.5\fnFanwood Text\i1\b0\fs70\frx8\fry3\c&H6B99AA&\3c&H1E3E4E&\4c&H070F1C&\bord1.5\shad2\t(\fs75)\move(419.2,718.6,372.8,734.6)}Súkromný inštitút\NShinra
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hovorím vám, videl som ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Na tom cintoríne bolo plno duchov!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Duchovia neexistujú.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pravdepodobne sa ti to len snívalo. Možno halucinácie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Asi si bol z toľkého učenia len unavený?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nechcel si povedať {\i1}smrteľne unavený{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To nie je nič smiešne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.08,Top,,0,0,0,,Ticho, Oyamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Začína hodina, sadnite si!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pozorne počúvajte,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo som to včera vlastne videl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:08.45,Top,,0,0,0,,Dneska tu mám nejaké novinky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Snívalo sa mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\frz270\fs60\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H616E5B&\4c&H72826C&\pos(1192.4,335.4)\fnSitka Small\alpha&H25&}Asakura Yoh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.06,Top,,0,0,0,,Máme tu nového prestupujúceho študenta... Asakura Yoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Z rodinných dôvodov sem prišiel až z Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Čo sa ti nepáči, Oyamada? Čo sa tváriš tak kyslo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Toto je ten človek, o ktorom som hovoril!\NTen, čo sa bavil s duchmi minulú noc!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Neexistuje nič také ako duchovia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okrem toho, kto si?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Čože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Takto nebudem vôbec schopný sa učiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H735862&\3c&H494244&\4c&HA9A8AA&\blur1.12\\fnExo\b0\pos(1585.6,189.2)}Obchod Saitou
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H695C7F&\3c&H434152&\4c&HA2AFC7&\blur1.12\\fnExo\b0\pos(1585.6,189.2)}Obchod Saitou
